hen compared to competitors) that can\nnonetheless yield reasonably accurate optical flow estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2023 16:17:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 May 2023 13:38:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
