Simulation results demonstrate that the proposed\nsolutions for MA-enhanced multiple access systems can significantly decrease\nthe total transmit power of users as compared to conventional FPA systems under\nboth perfect and imperfect field-response information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Feb 2023 11:16:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-15"}
